{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e90f1e3420","title":"恩格斯致卡尔·考茨基","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f9c1e282e3","index":0,"year":1891,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"e90f1e3420"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","name":"哥达纲领批判（人民出版社1971年版）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"马克思，人民出版社1971年版","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives4/main/0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"a80dd40419","name":"恩格斯"}]},"publication_details":{"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"94b1174913","type":"paragraph","text":"恩格斯致卡尔·考茨基","index":0,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"f8e281a807","type":"paragraph","text":"斯图加特","index":1,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"66b75b7ac1","type":"paragraph","text":"1891年1月15日于伦敦亲爱的男爵","index":2,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"53768d4ac1","type":"paragraph","text":"你从随信寄去的校样中可以看出，我不是不近人情的甚至还在序言中加了几滴使人镇静的吗啡和漠化钾，希望这对我们的朋友狄茨的多愁善感会起一定的抑制作用。今天我就给倍倍尔写信。以前我没有同他谈过这件事，因为我不愿意使他在季下克内西面前感到为难。那样，倍倍尔就有责任把这件事告诉季下克内西，而季下克内西一一从他在哈雷所做的关于党纲的讲话39来看，他已经从手稿中作了一些摘录——会采取一切办法阻揽手稿的发表。","index":3,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"7b74f7505f","type":"paragraph","text":"如果“实现自已的宗教需要，就象实现自己的肉体需要一样”这句话在文中不能保留，那就把加了着重号的几个字删掉，用省略号代替。这样，暗示就会更加微妙，而且仍然十分清楚。可以设想，这样一来，此处就不会引起怀疑。","index":4,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"0d56598740","type":"paragraph","text":"其他地方，我都按你们的要求做了，而且你看，甚至比你们要求的还多。","index":5,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"7593b13287","type":"paragraph","text":"你的弗·恩·","index":6,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"},{"id":"9071d144ab","type":"paragraph","text":"53","index":7,"publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420"}],"page":{"id":"baa8dd3ae3","publicationId":"0390c365-6951-4e70-9dc5-9f7aa4c900ab","articleId":"e90f1e3420","start":58,"end":58}}}},"__N_SSG":true}